Want to present at Tokyo Indies? You've come to the right place! Here's some things to know:

- presentations start around 8PM
- please make your presentation around 5 minutes in length
- most people present from their own laptop; if you would prefer for us to show a video or other file let us know in advance

The application form is [here](https://goo.gl/forms/msDrUsB3MuGDHss82). We look forward to hearing from you! ðŸŽ®

